The inside of this bag features 3 separate compartments total; 1 cell phone compartment with touch-screen window, 1 medium size pocket ideal for coins, cash, and cards, and 1 large microfiber lined pocket ideal for makeup, sunglasses, accessories and more.

This bag can be carried confidently in hand as a clutch by using the included removable wristlet strap, or worn on the shoulder or cross-body as a purse with the included removable and adjustable shoulder strap.
